      "review_summary": "The branch normalizes legacy OpenAI Codex OAuth auth-profile aliases, adds a metadata-only stale mode-mismatch auth diagnostic, adds regression coverage and a changelog entry, and currently also changes many unrelated generated, script, plugin, and formatting-only files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection on current main shows alias-only OpenAI Codex OAuth fields are not normalized before PI conversion, and stale api_key profile metadata can skip a stored OAuth credential before the generic missing-auth error.",
